text: Jolene Unsoeld (December 3, 1931 - November 28, 2021) was an American politician, who served as a member of the United States House of Representatives from 1989 to 1995. She represented the third congressional district of Washington as a Democrat. Unsoeld died on November 28, 2021, five days before her 90th birthday in Olympia, Washington. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1931 births Category:2021 deaths Category:United States representatives from Washington Category:Politicians from Oregon Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians
